_sText:
Hello, everyone!

ZIBA TOWER for CS:S is the reamake of Battlefield 3 "Ziba Tower".
This map was created and uploaded on Gamebanana.com by KENNITHH and finished by me. Thanks authors of de_resort & de_agency for their 3d models and textures which I use a lot on this map.
I hope you like my last remake.

All the best and good game!
